744. Int J Tuberc Lung Dis. 2018 Sep 1;22(9):991-999. doi: 10.5588/ijtld.17.0523.

Cost-utility analysis of high-dose treatment for intermediate-susceptible, 
dose-dependent tuberculosis patients.

Zuur MA(1), van Asselt ADI(2), van 't Boveneind-Vrubleuskaya N(3), Aleksa A(4), 
Postma MJ(2), Alffenaar JWC(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Clinical Pharmacy and Pharmacology, University Medical Centre 
