Long-term smoking cessation rates in elderly versus other adult smokers: A 
3-year follow-up study in Taiwan.

Hsu CL(1)(2)(3), Hsueh KC(1)(4), Chou MY(2)(5), Yu HC(1)(6), Mar GY(1)(7), Chen 
HJ(3), West R(8).

Author information:
(1)Department of Physical Examination Center, Kaohsiung Veterans General 
