(3)Department of Family Medicine, Kaohsiung Veterans General Hospital, Taiwan.
(4)Shu-Zen College of Medicine and Management, Kaohsiung, Taiwan.
(5)School of Medicine, National Yang-Ming University, Taiwan.
(6)Division of Gastroenterology, Department of Internal Medicine, Kaohsiung 
