Nanotechnological approaches for the development of herbal drugs in treatment of 
diabetes mellitus - a critical review.

Marella S(1), Tollamadugu NVKVP(2).

Author information:
(1)Nanotechnology Laboratory, Institute of Frontier Technology, Regional 
Agricultural Research Station, Acharya N. G. Ranga Agricultural University, 
