Value of hospital resources for effective pressure injury prevention: a 
cost-effectiveness analysis.

Padula WV(1), Pronovost PJ(2)(3), Makic MBF(4), Wald HL(5), Moran D(6), Mishra 
MK(7), Meltzer DO(8).

Author information:
(1)Health Policy & Management, Johns Hopkins Bloomberg School of Public Health, 
